An elderly couple was shot during an apparent house robbery in Lethabong, Edenvale on Wednesday.ER24 Spokesperson Chitra Bodasing Harduth said it is understood that the couple was shot while looking after their grandchildren at the property.&#8220;ER24 paramedics attended to the incident and found the woman seated at the back of a vehicle and the man limping on scene.&#8221;Harduth added that when the paramedics were assessing the woman&#8217;s injuries, she was found in a critical condition as she had been shot in the abdomen.The man was found to have sustained a gunshot wound to the left foot, the couple were than treated and transported to hospital for further medical care.The exact details surrounding the incident is yet unknown.&nbsp;-TNA Reporter